427
00:23:16,040 --> 00:23:18,090
The light here
reminds me of Tucson.

428
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:22,210
Tucson.
Is that a real place?

429
00:23:23,010 --> 00:23:25,100
Mmm-hmm. In Arizona.

430
00:23:25,140 --> 00:23:27,180
I always dream
of a little house there,
an adobe,

431
00:23:27,220 --> 00:23:30,170
and a-- and a horse.

432
00:23:30,210 --> 00:23:32,200
