433
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:35,060
No. It's where I got free.

434
00:23:37,140 --> 00:23:38,210
Got free?

435
00:23:41,070 --> 00:23:42,110
(Linda) Yeah.

436
00:23:42,150 --> 00:23:45,110
Society. Husband.

437
00:23:46,010 --> 00:23:47,130
Family.

438
00:23:47,170 --> 00:23:50,170
It's so beautiful there.
Desert.

439
00:23:50,210 --> 00:23:53,210
It's nature
all around you.

440
00:23:55,130 --> 00:23:58,150
When I was growing up
in liverpool...
Mmm.

441
00:23:58,190 --> 00:24:00,220
