into the woods

442
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:04,200
looking for frogs.

443
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:08,190
Frogs?
Mmm, frogs.

444
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:13,210
With me,
it was salamanders.

445
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:17,220
Salamanders, eh?
Mmm.

446
00:24:21,080 --> 00:24:22,180
That's nice.
Mmm-hmm.

447
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,190
