451
00:24:34,190 --> 00:24:37,020
Very kind
and loving, me mum.

452
00:24:37,060 --> 00:24:38,160
She used to say to me--

453
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:41,070
she used to say,
"hey, just let it be, son."

454
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:44,150
If I was upset
or something,
just let it be.

455
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:46,180
Mmm, what was her name?

456
00:24:47,130 --> 00:24:49,000
Mary.
Hmm.

457
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:50,220
Mary McCartney.

458
00:24:52,060 --> 00:24:53,220
Oh, she never said
a word to the doctors

459
00:24:54,020 --> 00:24:57,080
