461
00:24:59,220 --> 00:25:01,130
Typical nurse perhaps.

462
00:25:01,170 --> 00:25:04,050
Took care of everybody else
but not herself, you know?

463
00:25:05,190 --> 00:25:09,000
By the time they did
the mastectomy,
it was too late.

464
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,190
How old were you?

465
00:25:15,110 --> 00:25:16,200
14.

466
00:25:17,150 --> 00:25:19,080
Me brother was 12.

467
00:25:22,030 --> 00:25:25,200
And one terrible night,
US boys went down
the hospital.

468
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:29,080
Oh, they must have known
she was dying,

469
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:32,070
