487
00:26:50,230 --> 00:26:53,030
Whoa. That's hot.
Thank you.

488
00:26:54,050 --> 00:26:55,210
Mmm-hmm.

489
00:26:56,010 --> 00:26:58,200
When's the last time
you had a mammogram?

490
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:00,210
Mmm.
It's been a while.

491
00:27:01,010 --> 00:27:03,090
It is good and hot--
if ever.

492
00:27:04,010 --> 00:27:05,220
Uh, look, McCartney,

493
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:07,060
you got to get
this checked out.

494
00:27:07,100 --> 00:27:08,200
[Mumbling]

495
00:27:09,000 --> 00:27:12,030
Yeah. Yeah. I know.
Typical chrissie hynde.

496
00:27:13,060 --> 00:27:16,070
Hey, I don't want
to lose you.

497
00:27:16,110 --> 00:27:18,140
Promise you'll go
up to London
and see a specialist.

498
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:20,010
I promise.

499
00:27:20,050 --> 00:27:22,190
And tell your husband,
for god's sakes.

500
00:27:22,230 --> 00:27:25,010
I don't want him to worry.

501
00:27:35,200 --> 00:27:38,080
