00:43:27,200 --> 00:43:29,100
Why can't
we just live together?

792
00:43:31,060 --> 00:43:33,120
I want to settle down,

793
00:43:33,160 --> 00:43:35,130
have some kids of me own.

794
00:43:35,170 --> 00:43:37,120
Can a beatle ever
really settle down?

795
00:43:37,160 --> 00:43:39,020
I'm finished
sowing wild oats.

796
00:43:39,060 --> 00:43:42,000
I had all the girls I fancy.
